Proposed Idea: AI Powered Training Data Sanitizer

Core idea

•	6G uses AI models to manage network traffic.
•	These models have to learn from new data constantly to stay accurate as the environment changes.
•	This proposal adds a data sanitizer (whether small ML algo or other) into the O-RAN controller to act as a gatekeeper.
•	Every piece of data sent for training must pass through this sanitizer first.
•	It uses the De-Pois method to compare new data against a small set of known clean samples.
•	If the incoming data looks like a malicious outlier it is dropped before it can reach the primary AI model.
